<i>noun</i>: 일임 [이림], 위촉 [위촉] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>일임 [이림]</dt><br>
<dd>entrusting; leaving in another person's hands</dd><br>
<dd>일이나 권한 등을 모두 다 맡김.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of giving all of one's responsibilities, authority, etc. over to someone else.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>위촉 [위촉]</dt><br>
<dd>entrusting; commission</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 일을 남에게 부탁하여 맡김.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of asking someone to take charge of a task, and then leaving it in his/her hands.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>